<head>
<META NAME="ROBOTS" CONTENT="NOINDEX, NOFOLLOW">
<META NAME="ROBOTS" CONTENT="NOARCHIVE">
<title>Unblock Email</title>


</head>

<body>

<table border="0" align="center" style="border-collapse:collapse;width:450px;height:200px;" bordercolor="#111111">
  <tr>
    <td width="100%" valign="top"><font face="Verdana" size="2">WARNING - You are choosing to unblock an email address which has already unsubscribed from receiving further 
    sales, advertising or promotional content.<br><BR>You may only unblock this email address, 
    per customer consent, to send agreed upon content or update a customer about an ongoing transaction. 
    Sending additional emails with agreed upon content  will not violate the CAN-SPAM act.<br><br>
    <font color="#008000"><b>Block ID was released and recorded in the activity log. Close this message and refresh.</b></font></font></td>
  </tr>
</table>

</body>
</html>